OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine day with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine, though locally hazy at
OL,7,Ftimes. Hot or very hot during the
OL,8,Fafternoon, with light winds offering
OL,9,Flittle relief from the heat. Coastal
OL,10,Fareas will remain cooler as an onshore
OL,11,Fbreeze develops.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAnother warm or very warm
OL,14,Fnight for many, especially in urban
OL,15,Fareas and cities, while rural
OL,16,Flocations become noticeably cooler.
OL,17,FDry with light winds and largely clear
OL,18,Fskies throughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
