OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAnother hot day, with daytime
OL,6,Ftemperatures widely above average. Dry
OL,7,Fand predominantly sunny. Cooler along
OL,8,Fcoastal areas, with an onshore breeze.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,11,Fand largely sunny, though cooler, on
OL,12,FSaturday. Low cloud spreading widely
OL,13,Fovernight into Sunday, with brighter
OL,14,Fconditions developing later. Dry with
OL,15,Fplenty of sunshine on Monday, though
OL,16,Fturning cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
